spec_data.Name: perl-Class-Data-Accessor
spec_data.Description:
Class::Data::Accessor is the marriage of Class::Accessor and
Class::Data::Inheritable into a single module. It is used for creating
accessors to class data that overridable in subclasses as well as in class
instances.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:55:36 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Inheritable, overridable class and instance data accessor creation
